ygData.messageBody:
Hello,

There is a new survey for the eqenchanters community.

I thought this time I would make a little survey on everyone's favorite hard to obtain spell, Enchant Silver. Take a few seconds to fill it out!
-Sloop

----

Possible answers are:

o I obtained enchant silver by using Illusion: Dark Elf.
o I am a dark elf and purchased Enchant Silver.
o I payed another player who is a dark elf to buy it for me.
o I am below level 8.


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://www.onelist.com/surveycenter/eqenchanters


Thanks!

eqenchanters Owner
